  "title": "Basic Income, a new human right",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 1334.0,
      "end_time": 4374.0,
      "text": "Today austerity seems to be the only answer given"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 4374.0,
      "end_time": 6563.0,
      "text": "to remedy the economic crisis in Europe"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 6563.0,
      "end_time": 9151.0,
      "text": "yet people are getting poorer and poorer"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 9151.0,
      "end_time": 10662.0,
      "text": "Automation in manufacturing"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 10662.0,
      "end_time": 13112.0,
      "text": "and wealth accumulation by financial institutions"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 13112.0,
      "end_time": 15824.0,
      "text": "are changing our approach to work"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 15824.0,
      "end_time": 17045.0,
      "text": "More and more is produced"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 17045.0,
      "end_time": 19187.0,
      "text": "with fewer and fewer people"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 19187.0,
      "end_time": 20773.0,
      "text": "Unemployment rates have skyrocketed"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 20773.0,
      "end_time": 23812.0,
      "text": "and paid work is no longer a right for everyone!"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 23812.0,
      "end_time": 25726.0,
      "text": "The good news is that never before in history"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 25726.0,
      "end_time": 28474.0,
      "text": "have human societies generated so much wealth"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 28474.0,
      "end_time": 29452.0,
      "text": "But while this wealth is produced"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 29452.0,
      "end_time": 31832.0,
      "text": "by the work of all –past and present-"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 31832.0,
      "end_time": 33136.0,
      "text": "this wealth is unevenly"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 33136.0,
      "end_time": 35665.0,
      "text": "distributed among citizens"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 35665.0,
      "end_time": 37100.0,
      "text": "We, as European citizens"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 37100.0,
      "end_time": 38708.0,
      "text": "propose an alternative !"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 38708.0,
      "end_time": 40009.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not a new idea"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 40009.0,
      "end_time": 42386.0,
      "text": "but now is the time to put it into action !"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 42386.0,
      "end_time": 43150.0,
      "text": "It’s called"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 43150.0,
      "end_time": 46113.0,
      "text": "Unconditional Basic Income"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 46113.0,
      "end_time": 47675.0,
      "text": "Have you heard of it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 47675.0,
      "end_time": 49102.0,
      "text": "Not yet?"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 49102.0,
      "end_time": 51358.0,
      "text": "Article 25 of the Universal Declaration"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 51358.0,
      "end_time": 52779.0,
      "text": "of Human Rights states"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 52779.0,
      "end_time": 54938.0,
      "text": "Everyone has the right to a standard of living adequate"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 54938.0,
      "end_time": 57443.0,
      "text": "for the health and well-being of himself"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 57443.0,
      "end_time": 58605.0,
      "text": "and of his family"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 58605.0,
      "end_time": 59535.0,
      "text": "including food"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 59535.0,
      "end_time": 60140.0,
      "text": "clothing"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 60140.0,
      "end_time": 60710.0,
      "text": "housing"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 60710.0,
      "end_time": 61902.0,
      "text": "and medical care"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 61902.0,
      "end_time": 63847.0,
      "text": "and necessary social services"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 63847.0,
      "end_time": 66566.0,
      "text": "and the right to security in the event of unemployment..."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 66566.0,
      "end_time": 67446.0,
      "text": "There it is!"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 67446.0,
      "end_time": 68678.0,
      "text": "Basic Income should be"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 68678.0,
      "end_time": 69862.0,
      "text": "universal"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 69862.0,
      "end_time": 70986.0,
      "text": "individual"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 70986.0,
      "end_time": 72310.0,
      "text": "unconditional"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 72310.0,
      "end_time": 72986.0,
      "text": "and high enough"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 72986.0,
      "end_time": 74866.0,
      "text": "to ensure a dignified existence"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 74866.0,
      "end_time": 77394.0,
      "text": "and participation in society"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 77394.0,
      "end_time": 79699.0,
      "text": "This new fundamental right for humanity"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 79699.0,
      "end_time": 81638.0,
      "text": "not only would eradicate misery"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 81638.0,
      "end_time": 82954.0,
      "text": "it is also a way to develop"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 82954.0,
      "end_time": 84761.0,
      "text": "non-market oriented work"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 84761.0,
      "end_time": 85801.0,
      "text": "such as"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 85801.0,
      "end_time": 86877.0,
      "text": "artists"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 86877.0,
      "end_time": 87491.0,
      "text": "parents"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 87491.0,
      "end_time": 88871.0,
      "text": "and volunteers"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 88871.0,
      "end_time": 90749.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s also an economic measure!"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 90749.0,
      "end_time": 92187.0,
      "text": "A basic income for all"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 92187.0,
      "end_time": 95325.0,
      "text": "would mean supporting local business"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 95325.0,
      "end_time": 96816.0,
      "text": "Therefore, it would enable us"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 96816.0,
      "end_time": 100302.0,
      "text": "to fully exercise our citizenship"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 100302.0,
      "end_time": 101987.0,
      "text": "How do we finance it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 101987.0,
      "end_time": 102615.0,
      "text": "Easy!"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 102615.0,
      "end_time": 104640.0,
      "text": "We have several proposals"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 104640.0,
      "end_time": 107096.0,
      "text": "financial and high-income taxation"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 107096.0,
      "end_time": 110344.0,
      "text": "a consumption tax on luxury goods and polluting products"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 110344.0,
      "end_time": 111247.0,
      "text": "and mainly"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 111247.0,
      "end_time": 112406.0,
      "text": "self-financing"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 112406.0,
      "end_time": 114457.0,
      "text": "by simplification of a very long list"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 114457.0,
      "end_time": 116254.0,
      "text": "of current social transfers"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 116254.0,
      "end_time": 117958.0,
      "text": "and associated public services"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 117958.0,
      "end_time": 121099.0,
      "text": "which have become obsolete"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 121099.0,
      "end_time": 122179.0,
      "text": "What we propose"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 122179.0,
      "end_time": 123458.0,
      "text": "would be much simpler"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 123458.0,
      "end_time": 125346.0,
      "text": "equal and transparent"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 125346.0,
      "end_time": 127006.0,
      "text": "everyone gets a basic income"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 127006.0,
      "end_time": 129363.0,
      "text": "without even asking for it"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 129363.0,
      "end_time": 132859.0,
