    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 132859.0,
      "end_time": 134291.0,
      "text": "We, as European citizens"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 134291.0,
      "end_time": 136302.0,
      "text": "have now launched an official petition"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 136302.0,
      "end_time": 138406.0,
      "text": "called European Citizen Initiative"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 138406.0,
      "end_time": 139649.0,
      "text": "to make the European authorities"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 139649.0,
      "end_time": 142000.0,
      "text": "examine our manifesto"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 142000.0,
      "end_time": 145046.0,
      "text": "So... What&#39;s the deal?"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 145046.0,
      "end_time": 146307.0,
      "text": "First of all, we have to surpass"
